orpor was not expressed. The energy constraints experienced here by tube-nosed bats with relatively moderate Ta fluctuations, short commuting distances between roosting and feeding locations, and high availability of food were probably not substantial enough to require use of torpor.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Riek, Alexander", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "K\u00f6rtner, Gerhard", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Geiser, Fritz", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8cdab435a2cc2485cb4a8f3cb0fc7648", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/15b8845374df9117df62faaa786f089cb63b7028065a0fb656ef8084c4913b47", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/8B8VJCAT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/8B8VJCAT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/0829f98191a68f5305b383fa08c0cbdc!/b74253-76710", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "15", "pages": "2557-2564", "title": "Journal of Experimental Biology", "volume": "213"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8cdab435a2cc2485cb4a8f3cb0fc7648"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:8B8VJCAT"}, {"identifier": "10.1242/jeb.043182"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosysli